<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>WhatsBot CRM | WhatsApp Automation, Inbox, Campaigns, and AI</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Run WhatsApp campaigns, manage a shared inbox, automate replies, and operate your CRM from one WhatsBot dashboard.">
  <meta name="robots" content="index,follow">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0f766e">
  <link rel="canonical" href="<%= pageUrl %>">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:title" content="WhatsBot CRM">
  <meta property="og:description" content="A WhatsApp-first CRM with campaigns, inbox, automations, AI replies, integrations, and admin controls.">
  <meta property="og:image" content="<%= imageUrl %>">
  <meta property="og:url" content="<%= pageUrl %>">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="WhatsBot CRM">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Manage WhatsApp conversations, campaigns, AI workflows, and customer operations in one CRM.">
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="<%= imageUrl %>">
  <link rel="icon" href="/public/favicon.png">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');
    :root {
      --ink: #0f172a;
      --muted: #64748b;
      --line: #dbe4ea;
      --brand: #0f766e;
      --brand-strong: #115e59;
      --brand-soft: #ccfbf1;
      --paper: #f8fafc;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(20,184,166,0.12), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgba(15,118,110,0.10), transparent 22%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8fafc 52%, #eef6f5 100%);
    }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    .wrap { width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 32px)); margin: 0 auto; }
    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 22px 0;
    }
    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .brand-mark {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), #14b8a6);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(15,118,110,0.20);
    }
    .brand-title {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .brand-sub {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .link-btn, .primary-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 11px 16px;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;
    }
    .link-btn {
      color: #0f172a;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
    }
    .link-btn:hover, .primary-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .primary-btn {
      color: white;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), #14b8a6);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(15,118,110,0.18);
    }
    .hero {
      padding: 48px 0 72px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 32px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      border: 1px solid #cde7e3;
      color: var(--brand-strong);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    h1 {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5vw, 4.8rem);
      line-height: 0.98;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      margin: 18px 0 18px;
      max-width: 9ch;
    }
    .hero-copy {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #334155;
      max-width: 60ch;
    }
    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 26px;
    }
    .proof {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 26px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .proof span {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .hero-panel {
      position: relative;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
      border: 1px solid #d8ebe7;
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 22px;
      box-shadow: 0 22px 60px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-panel::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,184,166,0.08), transparent 45%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .status-strip {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      padding-bottom: 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #edf4f2;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .status-chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: #ecfdf5;
      color: #166534;
      border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
    }
    .dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #22c55e;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(34,197,94,0.14);
    }
    .metric-grid {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .metric {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 16px;
    }
    .metric-label {
      font-size: 0.74rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .metric-value {
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }
    .feature-list {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .feature-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #edf4f2;
      color: #334155;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .feature-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: var(--brand-soft);
      color: var(--brand-strong);
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }
    .section {
      padding: 0 0 72px;
    }
    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      align-items: end;
    }
    .section-kicker {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--brand-strong);
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 3rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      line-height: 1.04;
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 11ch;
    }
    .section-copy {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 58ch;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 0.96rem;
    }
    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.90);
      border: 1px solid #deebe8;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 22px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(15,23,42,0.04);
    }
    .card i {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: #ecfeff;
      color: #0f766e;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .cta {
      padding: 28px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #134e4a);
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 44px rgba(15,23,42,0.16);
    }
    .cta h2 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.8vw, 2.5rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }
    .cta p {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.80);
      line-height: 1.8;
      max-width: 56ch;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 24px 0 34px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(203,213,225,0.55);
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .hero, .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .section-head, .cta { align-items: flex-start; flex-direction: column; }
      h1, .section-title { max-width: none; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .nav { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px; }
      .nav-links, .hero-actions { width: 100%; }
      .nav-links a, .hero-actions a { flex: 1; }
      .metric-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .cta, .card, .hero-panel { border-radius: 22px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="wrap">
    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="/" class="brand" aria-label="WhatsBot home">
        <span class="brand-mark"><i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i></span>
        <span>
          <span class="brand-title">WhatsBot CRM</span>
          <span class="brand-sub">WhatsApp operations, campaigns, and AI</span>
        </span>
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a class="link-btn" href="/status"><i class="fas fa-heartbeat"></i>Status</a>
        <a class="link-btn" href="/qr"><i class="fas fa-qrcode"></i>Connect WhatsApp</a>
        <a class="primary-btn" href="/admin/login"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>Open CRM</a>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="wrap">
    <section class="hero">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow"><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>WhatsApp-first CRM</div>
        <h1>Run your customer pipeline inside chat.</h1>
        <p class="hero-copy">
          WhatsBot brings your shared inbox, campaigns, AI replies, contact scoring, automations, and admin controls into one operational dashboard built around WhatsApp conversations.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="primary-btn" href="/admin/login"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>Launch Admin Panel</a>
          <a class="link-btn" href="/status"><i class="fas fa-signal"></i>View Live Status</a>
        </div>
        <div class="proof">
          <span><i class="fas fa-comments"></i>Shared inbox</span>
          <span><i class="fas fa-bullhorn"></i>Campaign delivery</span>
          <span><i class="fas fa-robot"></i>AI workflows</span>
          <span><i class="fas fa-plug"></i>Backoffice integrations</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-panel" aria-label="WhatsBot feature summary">
        <div class="status-strip">
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:0.78rem;color:#64748b;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">Operations Snapshot</div>
            <div style="font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin-top:4px;">One control layer for the bot</div>
          </div>
          <div class="status-chip"><span class="dot"></span>CRM Ready</div>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-grid">
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="metric-label">Inbox</div>
            <div class="metric-value">Live</div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="metric-label">AI Modes</div>
            <div class="metric-value">3</div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="metric-label">Automation</div>
            <div class="metric-value">Rules</div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="metric-label">Channels</div>
            <div class="metric-value">WA+</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-list">
          <div class="feature-row">
            <span class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-inbox"></i></span>
            <span>Manage conversations, reply manually, and review contact history from the CRM inbox.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-row">
            <span class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-magic"></i></span>
            <span>Use Gemini, GPT, or Claude for AI replies, with local speech transcription and synthesis.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-row">
            <span class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i></span>
            <span>Run campaigns, scheduled messages, templates, integrations, audit logs, and user controls from one panel.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-head">
        <div>
          <div class="section-kicker">Built For Operations</div>
          <h2 class="section-title">The CRM side is the product.</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="section-copy">
          This is not just a bot runner. The backoffice is where teams manage live chats, orchestrate campaigns, enforce roles, review logs, and configure AI and integration behavior.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="cards">
        <div class="card">
          <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
          <h3>Shared Inbox & Contacts</h3>
          <p>Track every contact, inspect message history, reply from the panel, and manage tags, language, score, and follow-up context.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i>
          <h3>Campaigns & Scheduling</h3>
          <p>Create campaigns, schedule messages, manage templates, review delivery status, and keep outbound messaging organized.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <i class="fas fa-sliders-h"></i>
          <h3>Settings & Integrations</h3>
          <p>Configure AI providers, SMTP, inbound APIs, webhooks, Slack, Discord, auto-replies, logs, and bot operations from one place.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="cta">
        <div>
          <h2>Launch the CRM. Keep the bot under control.</h2>
          <p>Use the admin panel to manage production activity, or check the live status page before reconnecting the WhatsApp session.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="margin-top:0;">
          <a class="primary-btn" href="/admin/login"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>Admin Login</a>
          <a class="link-btn" href="/status" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.14);color:white;"><i class="fas fa-heartbeat"></i>Status</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="wrap footer">
    <div>WhatsBot CRM for WhatsApp automation, AI workflows, and customer operations.</div>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="/status">Status</a>
      <a href="/qr">QR Pairing</a>
      <a href="/admin/login">Admin Login</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/yaasiin-ayeva/WhatsBot" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
